AMLParameterObject.Title: Model selection only - WS
AMLParameterObject.Description: No description provided for this web service.

GlobalParameter.Name: Database query
GlobalParameter.DefaultValue: select FISCAL_WEEK, RGN_DESC, SUB_RGN_DESC, CTRY_DESC, CUST_TYPE_DESC, LOB_DESC, CORE_PREM, sum(FLD_SHP_UNTS) as total from POCdata where RGN_DESC='Americas' and SUB_RGN_DESC='United States and Canada' and CTRY_DESC='United States' and CUST_TYPE_DESC ='CBO SmallBusiness' and LOB_DESC = 'Personal Desktops' and CORE_PREM='core' and FISCAL_WEEK <= '201501' group by FISCAL_WEEK, RGN_DESC, SUB_RGN_DESC, CTRY_DESC, CUST_TYPE_DESC, LOB_DESC, CORE_PREM;
